33 Eigen::VectorXd DiscreteTransferFunction::update(const Eigen::VectorXd& pError)
34 {

56 void DiscreteTransferFunction::updateHistory()
57 {
58  Eigen::ArrayXXd lOutputHistory = Eigen::ArrayXXd::Zero(aNbTransferFunction, aFilterOrder);
59  Eigen::ArrayXXd lErrorHistory = Eigen::ArrayXXd::Zero(aNbTransferFunction, aFilterOrder + 1);
60  lOutputHistory.matrix().block(0, 1, aNbTransferFunction, aFilterOrder - 1) =
61  aOutputHistory.matrix().block(0, 0, aNbTransferFunction, aFilterOrder - 1);
62  lErrorHistory.matrix().block(0, 1, aNbTransferFunction, aFilterOrder) =
63  aErrorHistory.matrix().block(0, 0, aNbTransferFunction, aFilterOrder);
64  aOutputHistory = lOutputHistory;
65  aErrorHistory = lErrorHistory;
66 }

72 Eigen::VectorXd DiscreteTransferFunction::filterXOrder() const
73 {
74  Eigen::VectorXd lNumeratorResult = (aTransferFunctionCoefficient.aNumeratorFactor * aErrorHistory).rowwise().sum();
75  Eigen::VectorXd lDenominatorResult = (aTransferFunctionCoefficient.aDenominatorFactor * aOutputHistory).rowwise().sum();
76  return lNumeratorResult - lDenominatorResult;
77 }
